avvio: mongod --dbpath ~/mongodb/data/db --logpath ~/mongodb/log/mongo.log --logappend

show dbs -> mostra i db
use nomeDatabase -> seleziona il db
show collections -> mostra le collezioni

db.createUser({
    user: 'john',
    pwd: 'supersecretpassword',
    roles: 'readWrite'
})
-> per creare un utente

db.createCollection('nomecollection')
db.collection.remove({})
db.collection.insert({})

https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/method/db.createCollection/
https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/core/schema-validation/




##### mosquitto
mosquitto -> avvia il broker
mosquitto_sub -t 'stuff/topic' -> subscribe a topic
mosquitto_pub -t 'stuff/topic' -m 'message' -> send to topic